Dragonward Strike			KEY:Gray Hand Enforcer ~ Dragonward Strike			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ClassAbility.SpecialAttack.Supernatural	VISIBLE:YES	DEFINE:DragonwardStrike|0																		DESC:By calling upon the power of Ahghairon's dragonward, you can launch a mighty attack. %1 times per day you can make a melee attack with a +4 bonus on your attack roll and a damage bonus of %2. You must declare the strike before your roll the dice. Alternatively, you can use this power to boost a single casting of a spell as though it was effected by the Empower Spell Feat. These abilities are only usable within 10 miles of Waterdeep.|DragonwardStrike|GrayHandEnforcerLVL																																																																						SOURCEPAGE:p.78
