Weapon and Armor Proficiency	KEY:Knight of the Blue Moon ~ Weapon and Armor Proficiency	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ClassAbility.SpecialQuality			VISIBLE:YES																							DESC:You gain no proficiency with any weapons, armor, or shield. Selune's favored weapon is the heavy mace, which Knights of the Blue Moon refer to as the moon's hand. Mystra prefers shuriken, which they call whirlstars.																																																																																																																	SOURCEPAGE:p.81
Moon Blessing			KEY:Knight of the Blue Moon ~ Moon Blessing			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ClassAbility.SpecialQuality.Supernatural	VISIBLE:YES																							DESC:During days and nights of the waning or new moon, you can channel Selune's influence over the weave to reduce the impact of magic directed against you. At the cost of a turn undead attempt, you receive a sared bonus of +%1 on a single saving throw or spell-like ability. You can use this as an immediate action. During days and nights of the waxing or full moon, you can increase the effect of magic cast by you. At the cost of a turn undead attempt, you increase your save DC of a single spell or spell-like ability by +%1. Using this ability is a swift action.|Knight of the Blue MoonLVL																																																		SOURCEPAGE:p.81
